{"tid":2462594,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"澳洲繼續承認BNO申請WH 日韓意紐向外媒表示BNO仍然有效","createTime":"2021-03-26T05:51:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-26T06:47:53.000Z","uid":21470,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"493652a3a5796fde1a7845e3642a8afa7b14078f","tid":2462594,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T05:51:23.000Z","msg":"BNO｜澳洲續承認BNO持有人申請工作假期<br />\n<br />\n特區政府發言人表示，由於港府已不承認英國BNO護照作為有效旅行證件及身份證明，工作假期計劃下的香港參加者，只限於香港特區護照持有人，特區政府已透過駐港總領事館，正式知會14個與本港簽訂工作假期計劃協議的國家。 英國外交部發言人說，香港政府無權決定外國政府承認哪些護照有效，英國會繼續視BNO為有效旅遊證件，並繼續發行。澳洲內政部說，無法回應港府可能提出的任何建議，強調澳洲簽證的申請要求，已列明在部門網站。根據內政部的工作假期簽證網站，簽證的申請人必須是來自19個國家或地區的公民，包括持有BNO的香港居民。<br />\n<br />\n路透社早前引述西方外交人員報道，很多國家都不理會特區政府的要求，認為只是港府試探，港府無權要求任何國家承護哪些護照；亦有外交官表示，港府舉動接近挑釁，指香港作為國際金融中心，這種並非香港政府以往的行事方式。 <br />\n<br />\n部份同本港達成工作假期協議的國家，例如日本、南韓、意大利及新西蘭向外電證實，仍然承認BNO作為申請簽證的旅行證件。南韓外交部指未收到港府信件，有收到信件的匈牙利表示，開始商討修改工作假期計劃。目前未知美國是否收到信件，國務院發言人指，仍然承認BNO作申請簽證的證件。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2384613\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2384613&d=eMoIgPJs71q5KSiTXOS1GpNY2w26zYPSLCKwhaLFqs8%3D&h=138c2beb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2384613</a>"},{"pid":"382da48e49453fcdc638498731919d387490a9ba","tid":2462594,"uid":129169,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T05:52:01.000Z","msg":"香港政苦好撚7<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92d83b13d7c5e93d08689477c4087453c1caea38","tid":2462594,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T05:52:27.000Z","msg":"面係人地俾，架係自己丟"},{"pid":"729ce7f1e4bf3bb9378f2ec9460e9c394259a611","tid":2462594,"uid":146030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T05:53:16.000Z","msg":"美國都冇wh<br />\n所以咪收唔到信囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41aec9d702e8755a7d832a66121f1432960debb1","tid":2462594,"uid":23221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T05:53:18.000Z","msg":"香港政府柒撚到呢."},{"pid":"8c2ab7755fbc37abd4f93fc79f9d0c40b83b3204","tid":2462594,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T05:54:04.000Z","msg":"點解港共可以咁柒"},{"pid":"aea168da070d5f1e125156cc11d7b993e46db8d3","tid":2462594,"uid":1643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T06:04:26.000Z","msg":"然後西方: 777 再嘈就唔承認支那護照就好笑 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"043a3c9f7624d67acb8d6d614d7afbc1d1aa08ed","tid":2462594,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T06:06:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />港共今次柒到喊"},{"pid":"f8ae9db8a7319e5c002a6283fdd5f42f30bdb7d4","tid":2462594,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T06:07:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />藍絲手足 輸了"},{"pid":"37ff676159573ca47445cd727538410a501504a8","tid":2462594,"uid":8171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T06:08:15.000Z","msg":"大巴大巴星鳩死柒婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2933588b29d25f9326766b091d43ce9445451fd3","tid":2462594,"uid":103325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T06:12:38.000Z","msg":"再嘈多兩嘈，一陣人地取消你特區護照免簽，或者調返轉唔承認你特區護照，咁就真係搞撚笑啦"},{"pid":"57d464bf2d3ccc790a2453148b9380485e3aee15","tid":2462594,"uid":192517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T06:45:00.000Z","msg":"匈牙利歐洲